  <Name>ufbx SDK</Name>
  <!-- Software Name and Version  -->
<!-- Software Name: ufbx SDK
    Download Link: https://github.com/ufbx/ufbx/releases/tag/v0.21.2
    Version: 0.21.2
    Notes: In the initial request for ufbx, I answered 'Internal' to the question 'Is this product only used internally?'. However, I am not sure what this meant. Therefore, since the user will be able to select uFBX to be used as the SDK to load FBX files, I assumed that I should have answered 'Consumer Facing'.
Additionally, I selected 'Yes' tp the question 'Will functionality regarding TPS Submission be strictly offline?'. As I assumed this meant the SDK was only internally used by the editor. No external access.
Note that the code of the uFBX SDK is not in the Restricted folder so accessible to licenceses.
        -->
<Location>//Fortnite/Main/Engine/Plugins/Interchange/Runtime/Source/Parsers/ThirdParty/uFBX/0.21.2/</Location>
<Function>This library provides an interface to interpret the FBX file format</Function>
<Eula>https://github.com/ufbx/ufbx/blob/master/LICENSE</Eula>
